*Fred Kay – engineer on &quot;Turnaround&quot;, &quot;D-7&quot;, &quot;Son of a Gun&quot;, and &quot;Molly&#x27;s Lips&quot;
*Craig Montgomery – production, engineer on &quot;Aneurysm&quot; and &quot;Even in His Youth&quot;
*Andy Wallace – mixing on &quot;Aneurysm&quot; and &quot;Even in His Youth&quot;

